The,VerticalResponse,REST,API,allows,developers,to,utilize,its,marketing,tools,in,their,own,applications,so,that,end,users,can,manage,marketing,campaign,contacts,organize,contacts,into,lists,post,or,send,social,media,messages,or,emails,and,collect,statistics,on,those,messages,This,API,is,only,compatible,with,VR,VerticalResponse,provides,online,marketing,tools,for,use,over,email,and,social,media,channels,with,messages,optimized,for,use,on,desktop,computers,and,mobile,devices